Class DisplayedSudoku

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • sudoku.gui.model.DisplayedSudoku
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DisplayData

    public class DisplayedSudoku
extends java.util.Observable
implements DisplayData
    The data that is displayed by the GUI with the option to convert it into a Board and solve it.
